If you mez the bonedancer and charge the pets, the healing pets kite you.  I also can not &quot;one shot&quot; the healer pet when I do catch up to it.   The pets are tougher if the bd summons only 3 pets vs. 4 pets.   If just summons 3 pets the healers will be green instead of gray.  You must of fought a bd who is inexperienced.<br>
